OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781385839
OL,3,CHedgehog in a prickle after getting
OL,4,Cwedged in a garden gate
OL,6,FA hedgehog was found in a prickly
OL,7,Fsituation, firmly wedged in the ornate
OL,8,Fmetalwork of a garden gate in South
OL,9,FOxfordshire.
OL,11,FThe female hedgehog, now
OL,12,Faffectionately named Ivy, was
OL,13,Fdiscovered early one morning by a
OL,14,Fconcerned homeowner in Drayton St
OL,15,FLeonard, Wallingford.
OL,17,FShe spotted the spiny mammal trapped
OL,18,Fbetween the bars of her garden gate
OL,19,Fand despite her best efforts, she was
OL,20,Funable to free it.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
