PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781385839
OL,3,CHedgehog in a prickle after getting
OL,4,Cwedged in a garden gate
OL,6,FDetermined to save it, she carefully
OL,7,Fremoved the entire gate from its
OL,8,Fhinges and transported both the gate
OL,9,Fand the prickly passenger in the back
OL,10,Fof her car to Tiggywinkles Wildlife
OL,11,FHospital.
OL,13,FThe hospital's veterinary team carried
OL,14,Fthe gate, complete with attached
OL,15,Fhedgehog, into the preparation room.
OL,17,FIvy was gently anaesthetised to
OL,18,Fminimise stress and allow staff to
OL,19,Fsafely manoeuvre her free from the
OL,20,Fmetalwork.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781385839
OL,3,CHedgehog in a prickle after getting
OL,4,Cwedged in a garden gate
OL,6,FIvy escaped the ordeal without any
OL,7,Fserious injuries and after spending
OL,8,Fseveral days resting and recovering
OL,9,Funder the care of the Tiggywinkles
OL,10,Fteam, she was successfully released
OL,11,Fback into the wild close to where she
OL,12,Fwas found.
OL,14,FA spokesperson for Tiggywinkles
OL,15,Fsaid:"This was certainly one of the
OL,16,Fmore unusual admissions we've had. We
OL,17,Fare incredibly grateful to Ivy's
OL,18,Frescuer, whose determination and
OL,19,Fingenuity ensured she received the
OL,20,Fhelp she needed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
