PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781385839
OL,3,CHedgehog in a prickle after getting
OL,4,Cwedged in a garden gate
OL,6,F"Rather than risking injury by forcing
OL,7,Fher free, she brought the entire gate
OL,8,Fto us ` and that decision undoubtedly
OL,9,Fhelped achieve such a positive
OL,10,Foutcome."
OL,12,FTiggywinkles is reminding members of
OL,13,Fthe public to regularly check gardens
OL,14,Fand fences for wildlife hazards,
OL,15,Fparticularly during the busy summer
OL,16,Fmonths when hedgehogs are actively
OL,17,Ftravelling between feeding and nesting
OL,18,Fsites.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
